<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.4.1">
<l>kāvār maṭalpeṇṇai yaṉṟi larikuralum</l>
<l>ēvāyi ṉūṭiyaṅku meḵkiṉ koṭitālō</l>
<l>pūvār maṇamkamaḻum pullāṇi kaitoḻutēṉ</l>
<l>pāvā yitunamakkōr pāṉmaiyē yākātē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh, the intermittent call of the black ibis in the palm</l>
<l rend="indent">whose leaves spread over the garden</l>
<l>Is truly as cruel as a weapon which pierces into an arrow wound!</l>
<l>I worship, hands [joined], in Pullāṇi, where the scent of flowers wafts.</l>
<l>Lady, will this [suffering] not become a custom for us?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
